-N-3Y8NVNDFhQ79x7B6-.text: Incident reported at 4750 Grand Ave S.

-N-3Zop80Djya63Ijr8N.text: Firefighters on the scene have confirmed that smoke can be seen from a restaurant.

-N-3_FHVgeGiCbPM8egv.text: Firefighters are attempting to enter the building.

-N-3aOkN_JNKYStbCpt5.text: Firefighters on the scene say they have a fire on the roof of the restaurant.

-N-3b8K1uPUCkG7rq8nR.text: Firefighters confirm that they have a fire in the kitchen wall.

-N-3byBpx72PtyScgTmt.text: Firefighters at the scene advise they have extinguished the fire. They are conducting a search to see if the fire spread.

-N-3caJZ7D_SVIocvZfm.text: Firefighters say they have shut down the gas in the building. They are searching for anyone possibly trapped.

-N-3fQaTeW-Ez_-7GgH8.text: Firefighters have searched the premises and have not located anyone who was trapped or injured. They are conducting more searches into the restaurant.

-N-3hB-dwU5O8tqBYQzr.text: Firefighters have conducted a more thorough search and have not located any injured victim.

-N-3ii-1dFOuG160ntxG.text: Firefighters have confirmed that the fire is under control.
